                                <div class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                                    <p>Culture operates on a spectrum from constructive to destructive forces. The logical structure of an algebraic equation ideally reflects these dynamics. The objective is defined on one side, while the enablers (numerator) and disablers (denominator) define how it will be achieved. By maximizing enablers and minimizing disablers, the objective is realized.</p>
                                </div>
